These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, cain
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, classical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, cricket
1. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Cigar           | cain | vegafina |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | classical  |
| Sport     | baseball      | cricket     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, disaster
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower          | tulip | daffodil |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | disaster         |
| Beverage           | 7up     | cola         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, october
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, thai
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower
1. the thai is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| Birthday           | october | september     |
| Nationality   | japanese            | thai         |
| Flower     | balloon-flower         | dahlia   |

 #################################

 
