The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, librarian
City: hamburg, new-york
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, rowing
1. the dressmaker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
3. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Game         | billiard | scrabble |
| Job           | librarian     | dressmaker |
| City   | hamburg      | new-york    |
| Sport           | rowing          | badminton       |

