1. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the fan of country is on the far right##1
3. the canadian is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |
| Pet      | lizard         | dog         |
| Nationality   | canadian      | japanese      |
| Music-Genre         | disco | country |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing    | card-games           |

