.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
2 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, scientist
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the scientist##1
4. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby      | singing     | magic-tricks |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Game   | scrabble     | monopoly     |
| Job     | freelancer | scientist     |

 